<br>
but uh, am I the only one who feels really shortchanged in the illusion department? iksar illusion was a token illusion we had to get as it's a race and we get all those... and hell we had some really really really overly tough quest for its level. same will hold true for kerran...although maybe they've learned their lesson and it's just sold somewhere. the question in my mind is, will we see another illusion?<br>
<br>
we haven't got one aside from token iksar yet (although I didn't play when EQ was first released, don't know if they added any early on)... we were blatantly lied to and said they wouldn't give us spectre illusion cause of global memory or something like that (increased loading time), then they go and give necros that. shamen get bear form...what's next? :P<br>
